14:
Well, of course I am! The concert's
today!
17:
I do wish everyone else was here
too, but... I'm ready to do what I can!
We should have a decent crowd
from the tissue promotion.
21:
I bet we will. We worked our butts off,
after all!
24: We'll support you however we can.
34:
M-monsters popped up outta
nowhere and started swarming the
food!
43:
What do you think you're doing?!
Bad monster! BAD!
44:
Look at how much trouble you're
causing for everyone! Shame on
you! Now scram! Shoo!
48:
That is NOT SAFE! Get back! We can
handle this!
64:
This isn't the time to be
complimenting her wrestling moves!
75:
Phew... That should be all of them. 
I think we're in the clear.
77:
Thank you so, so much... Not a single
one of us got hurt because of your
efforts.
79:
But I don't think there's any
salvaging the event...
82:
I can help with the clean up and
prep! Just please... Don't cancel the
concert!
84:
Well, the thing is... We might have
trouble convincing people to show
up, considering all the hubbub.
88:
Then I'll head to town and let
everyone know the concert's still on!
89:
I'm sure they'll come, now that it's
completely safe!
93:
Come join us at Burger Karatsu!
We've got a huge event today, and
you won't want to miss it!
97:
The monster situation has been
taken care of. Rest assured, your
safety is guaranteed.
101:
I appreciate the assist, Stella. We'll
reel them in yet!
105: I am more than happy to help.
111:
To be fair... The old me would've
given up at the first sign of trouble.
113:
But the idol I wanna be now would
never let anything keep her down!
119:
Ahaha, I'm just parroting what
Ai-chan said before though.
121:
Anyway, let's keep going! We've still
got a little more time until the event
starts!
125:
We did all we could. Hopefully it was
enough...
128:
I am certain at least a few people
will come.
133:
Well, even if it's not ideal, I'll do my
best! Just watch me!
136:
Of course. My eyes will be trained on
you.
140:
There you are! Better hurry and get
changed—crowd's been waiting!
144:
So some people did show up! Thank
goodness... I'll go get dressed!
147:
Some? Didn't you just hear me say
"crowd"? We've got a full house!
159: Why... do you guys look exhausted?
162:
I went to Palpebra to do a bit of
advertising on my own. Couldn't let
you two do all the work, you know?
164:
Tatsumi came up to help about
halfway through.
169:
I just happened to be passing by.
Besides, it'd be a waste to cancel
the event I prepped so much for!
179:
HEY! Who gave you permission to
stand around doing nothing? You
have a performance to put on!
184: Go on. We will be watching.
189:
Yeah... Yeah! Stella, kick back and
enjoy the show!
191:
I'll do my best to shine like the idol 
I want to be!
200:
Sorry to keep you waiting! 
It's about time we kicked things off!
